{"id":116,"ayahs":[{"number":46,"arabic":"وَقَفَّيْنَا عَلَىٰٓ ءَاثَٰرِهِم بِعِيسَى ٱبْنِ مَرْيَمَ مُصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ مِنَ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ ۖ وَءَاتَيْنَٰهُ ٱلْإِنجِيلَ فِيهِ هُدًۭى وَنُورٌۭ وَمُصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ مِنَ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ وَهُدًۭى وَمَوْعِظَةًۭ لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ","translation":"And We caused Jesus, the son of Mary, to follow in the footsteps of those [earlier prophets], confirming the truth of whatever there still remained of the Torah; and We vouchsafed unto him the Gospel, wherein there was guidance and light, confirming the truth of whatever there still remained of the Torah, and as a guidance and admonition unto the God-conscious.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/715.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":45989,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَفَّيْنَا","translation":"এবং পিছনে পাঠিয়েছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45990,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45991,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَاثَـٰرِهِم","translation":"পদচিহ্নের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45992,"position":4,"arabic":"بِعِيسَى","translation":"ঈসাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45993,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱبْنِ","translation":"পুত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45994,"position":6,"arabic":"مَرْيَمَ","translation":"মারইয়ামের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45995,"position":7,"arabic":"مُصَدِّقًۭا","translation":"সত্যায়নকারীরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45996,"position":8,"arabic":"لِّمَا","translation":"তার যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45997,"position":9,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45998,"position":10,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"হাতের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45999,"position":11,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46000,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ ۖ","translation":"তাওরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46002,"position":13,"arabic":"وَءَاتَيْنَـٰهُ","translation":"ও আমরা দিয়েছি তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46003,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنجِيلَ","translation":"ইঞ্জিল","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46004,"position":15,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"মধ্যে তার(ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46005,"position":16,"arabic":"هُدًۭى","translation":"পথনির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46006,"position":17,"arabic":"وَنُورٌۭ","translation":"ও আলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46007,"position":18,"arabic":"وَمُصَدِّقًۭا","translation":"এবং (ইঞ্জিলও) সত্যায়নকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46008,"position":19,"arabic":"لِّمَا","translation":"তার যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46009,"position":20,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46010,"position":21,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"হাতের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46011,"position":22,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46012,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ","translation":"তওরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46013,"position":24,"arabic":"وَهُدًۭى","translation":"এবং পথনির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46014,"position":25,"arabic":"وَمَوْعِظَةًۭ","translation":"ও উপদেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46015,"position":26,"arabic":"لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ","translation":"জন্যে মুত্তাকীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_046_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46016,"position":27,"arabic":"٤٦","translation":"(৪৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":47,"arabic":"وَلْيَحْكُمْ أَهْلُ ٱلْإِنجِيلِ بِمَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ فِيهِ ۚ وَمَن لَّمْ يَحْكُم بِمَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ فَأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْفَٰسِقُونَ","translation":"Let, then, the followers of the Gospel judge in accordance with what God has revealed therein: for they who do not judge in the light of what God has bestowed from on high-it is they, they who are truly iniquitous!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/716.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":46627,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلْيَحْكُمْ","translation":"এবং (নির্দেশ ছিলো) যেন বিচার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46628,"position":2,"arabic":"أَهْلُ","translation":"অনুসারীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46629,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنجِيلِ","translation":"ইঞ্জিলের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46630,"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَآ","translation":"সেই অনুসারে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46631,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46632,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46633,"position":7,"arabic":"فِيهِ ۚ","translation":"মধ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46635,"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46636,"position":9,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46637,"position":10,"arabic":"يَحْكُم","translation":"বিচার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46638,"position":11,"arabic":"بِمَآ","translation":"তা দিয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46639,"position":12,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46640,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46641,"position":14,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"তবে ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46642,"position":15,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46643,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْفَـٰسِقُونَ","translation":"সত্যত্যাগী","audioUrl":"wbw/005_047_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46644,"position":17,"arabic":"٤٧","translation":"(৪৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":48,"arabic":"وَأَنزَلْنَآ إِلَيْكَ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ بِٱلْحَقِّ مُصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ مِنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَمُهَيْمِنًا عَلَيْهِ ۖ فَٱحْكُم بَيْنَهُم بِمَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ ۖ وَلَا تَتَّبِعْ أَهْوَآءَهُمْ عَمَّا جَآءَكَ مِنَ ٱلْحَقِّ ۚ لِكُلٍّۢ جَعَلْنَا مِنكُمْ شِرْعَةًۭ وَمِنْهَاجًۭا ۚ وَلَوْ شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ لَجَعَلَكُمْ أُمَّةًۭ وَٰحِدَةًۭ وَلَٰكِن لِّيَبْلُوَكُمْ فِى مَآ ءَاتَىٰكُمْ ۖ فَٱسْتَبِقُوا۟ ٱلْخَيْرَٰتِ ۚ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ مَرْجِعُكُمْ جَمِيعًۭا فَيُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ فِيهِ تَخْتَلِفُونَ","translation":"And unto thee [O Prophet] have We vouchsafed this divine writ, setting forth the truth, confirming the truth of whatever there still remains of earlier revelations and determining what is true therein. Judge, then, between the followers of earlier revelation in accordance with what God has bestowed from on high, and do not follow their errant views, forsaking the truth that has come unto thee. Unto every one of you have We appointed a [different] law and way of life. And if God had so willed, He could surely have made you all one single community: but [He willed it otherwise] in order to test you by means of what He has vouchsafed unto, you. Vie, then, with one another in doing good works! Unto God you all must return; and then He will make you truly understand all that on which you were wont to differ.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/717.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":47272,"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنزَلْنَآ","translation":"এবং (হে নাবী)অবতীর্ণ করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47273,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْكَ","translation":"প্রতি তোমার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47274,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47275,"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ","translation":"সহকারে সত্য","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47276,"position":5,"arabic":"مُصَدِّقًۭا","translation":"সত্যায়নকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47277,"position":6,"arabic":"لِّمَا","translation":"তার যা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47278,"position":7,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47279,"position":8,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"হাতের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47280,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47281,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"সেই কিতাবের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47282,"position":11,"arabic":"وَمُهَيْمِنًا","translation":"ও সংরক্ষকরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47283,"position":12,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ ۖ","translation":"উপর তার","audioUrl":"wbw/005_048_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47285,"position":13,"arabic":"فَٱحْكُم","translation":"অতএব বিচার করো","audioUrl"